title: Joyous about election
text: I feel really joyous about the results of the election. I'm so glad that I haver always supported Joe Biden, and that Kamala Harris was my pick for vice president. I thought it would turn out this way, but of course faith is challenged along the way.

title: Liking my Alexa
text: I love talking to my Echo. Alexa is like a loyal but dumb companion.
